title: Dividend Champion, Contender, And Challenger Highlights: Week Of March 12
description: A weekly summary of dividend activity for Dividend Champions, Contenders, and Challengers. Companies which changed their dividends. Companies with upcoming ex-dividend dates.

title: Where Will Oracle Stock Be in 1 Year?
description: Oracle (NYSE: ORCL) posted its latest earnings report on March 9.  That slowdown is minor, but it indicates that Oracle isn't immune to the cooler software spending that hurt Amazon, Microsoft, and Alphabet's Google over the past year.

title: I built an ADU in my backyard that brings in $3,000 a month. Now I urge other California homeowners to do the same.
description: Joyce Higashi rents her tiny home out to traveling nurses for three months at a time. In her spare time, the "ADU evangelist" spreads the word on how she did it.
